          "systemMessage": "=const visualPrompt = `Convert this Turkish LinkedIn post into an English visual prompt for Nanobanana.\n\nANALYZE CONTENT LENGTH & CREATE APPROPRIATE VISUAL:\n\nSHORT POST (< 500 chars):\n- Quote-style graphic: Feature key statement with large typography\n- Minimal icons, clean background\n- Focus on 1 main message\n\nMEDIUM POST (500-1200 chars):\n- Mini infographic: 3-4 key points with icons\n- Each point: icon + 1 short sentence\n- Compact, focused layout\n\nLONG POST (> 1200 chars):\n- Full infographic: Multiple sections with data visualization\n- Charts, statistics, detailed visual storytelling\n- Comprehensive layout\n\nCORE REQUIREMENTS:\n- ALL TEXT IN ENGLISH (headers, labels, branding)\n- Content-specific visuals (AI→tech imagery, health→medical symbols)\n- Color variety: purple, green, orange, teal (avoid blue dominance)\n- 16:9 format, LinkedIn-optimized\n- Bottom branding: \"Botfusions | info@botfusions.com\" (LARGE, readable - 15% image height)\n- High contrast text, mobile-friendly\n- NO text on main visual area\n\nSTYLE: Modern, professional, photorealistic or flat-design. Match visual complexity to post length.\n\nOUTPUT: Only the image prompt, no quotes or explanations.\n\nPOST (MAX 1900 CHARS):\n{{ ($json.contentSnippet || $json.content || '').replace(/<[^>]*>/g, '').substring(0, 2000) }}"
